{"tid":1137113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜收恐嚇信　高雄警方發現網絡留言IP來自香港","createTime":"2019-05-03T13:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T17:29:47.000Z","uid":164771,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ff354d4f9341ab7773b7ddd7c90ef0000d5fe6","tid":1137113,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"台灣高雄市長韓國瑜接連收到恐嚇信，警方偵辦發現網絡留言IP來自香港，但未查出疑犯，初步相信恐嚇信來自境內，研判並非出自同一人，將持續追查。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒引述高雄市政府警察局刑事警察大隊隊長侯東輝表示，恐嚇信雖然有指紋，但指紋都不全，信件上的筆跡亦無疑犯可供比對，案件將循恐嚇危害安全等罪方向偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，連日來警方有規劃加強保護韓國瑜及其家人。"},{"pid":"5a7894bb9ee075b31143f8001fc6e6b462484d3f","tid":1137113,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c72e32c5b392ac375758d30689c7dd19fe7515f","tid":1137113,"uid":66260,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"又IP又指紋即係點撚樣呀?<br />\n垃圾記者百幾字既新聞都寫到一舊舊咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30b105f63b1a9f38e963133f74bbcd137fbd0ea","tid":1137113,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"台灣啲警察咁垃圾<br />\n查乜都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e9be3ef1156f97b1ca21d849ee68590c58127a","tid":1137113,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"杜德偉？"},{"pid":"5565c5167244305d1ac07bdebd77fe35ec16d18b","tid":1137113,"uid":41988,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"用vpn 火星都得啦"},{"pid":"461971ee480d1c437c9462d1620b5df8f717e63d","tid":1137113,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"自編自導自演？"},{"pid":"4a72fbe234ba62db8f61b4607710a5a265710be2","tid":1137113,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"好似想支持通過逃犯條例喎<img src=\"/assets/